### Hadith 3:523

*Narrated 'Amr:*

I said to Tawus, "I wish you would give up Mukhabara (Share-cropping),
for the people say that the Prophet forbade it." On that Tawus replied,
"O 'Amr! I give the land to share-croppers and help them. No doubt; the
most learned man, namely Ibn 'Abbas told me that the Prophet had not
forbidden it but said, 'It is more beneficial for one to give his land
free to one's brother than to charge him a fixed rental."

